Discriminative models → Learn decision boundary → Predict label given input
Generative models → Learn data distribution → Can generate new data

| Feature          | Discriminative           | Generative      |
| ---------------- | ------------------------ | --------------- |
| Learns           | P(y | x)                 | P(x, y) or P(x) |
| Goal             | Classification           | Data generation |
| Output           | Label                    | New samples     |
| Complexity       | Lower                    | Higher          |
| Data Requirement | Less                     | More            |
| Examples         | Logistic Regression, SVM | GAN, VAE, GPT   |
